# Local-only test artefacts at the repo root. Nothing under `/tests`
# is committed: `tests/harness` is an independent sub-workspace
# (its own Cargo.toml `[workspace]`) for host integration tests,
# and `tests/hardware` holds rig configs that depend on operator
# environment. The main build does not depend on anything here.
# The leading `/` anchors the pattern to the repo root so
# `tools/tests/` (cargo integration tests for the host tools) is
# not affected.
/tests/
/tools/tests/

# Host-test shims for excluded (non-workspace) module crates generate
# their own lockfile; not tracked (the crates carry no host-test deps).
modules/**/Cargo.lock
